EZ - IN: Spoiler warning
Do one of the following:
  • Get an A rank or higher [[尊師 ～The Guru～]] while getting 6 or fewer Bad and Miss judgements combined
  • Get an A rank on [[尊師 ～The Guru～]], then do one of the following:

    • Play [[Reimei]] or [[尊師 ～The Guru～]] while getting 6 or fewer Bad and Miss judgements combined

Rrharil.title: Rrhar'il
Rrharil.unlock:
EZ - IN: Spoiler warning
  1. Get an A rank or higher on [[Chronos Collapse - La Campanella]]
  2. Play [[Clock Paradox]] on the same difficulty. A clock image will flash before the final drop. After this image appears, do not miss any notes.
  3. [[Chronostasis]] will play within a after version of the song select menu. Get an A rank or higher.
  4. [[Glaciaxion]] will play after a glitched version of the song select menu. Get a V rank or higher.
  5. Rrhar'il will play after a cutscene. Get a C rank or higher.
If you fail on steps 3~5, repeat from step 2.
AT: Get an S rank or higher on Rrhar'il [IN]

Crave Wave.unlock:
Spoiler warning:
  1. Get an A rank or higher on [[Rrhar'il]]>
  2. Open Chapter 8
  3. Play [[micro.wav]]. Crave Wave will play instead. Get an S rank or higher to unlock.

The Chariot ~REVIIVAL~.unlock:
Spoiler warning:
  1. Unlock [[Crave Wave]]
  2. Play [[Cereris]]. The Chariot ~REVIIVAL~ will play instead. Get an S rank or higher.
  3. [[Retribution]] will play automatically, followed by [[DESTRUCTION 3,2,1]]. DESTRUCTION 3,2,1 has ended, all three will unlock.

Luminescence.unlock:
Spoiler warning:
  1. Unlock [[The Chariot ~REVIIVAL~]]
  2. Select The Chariot ~REVIIVAL~ in Chapter 8. Do not play the chart.
  3. Turn your device upside-down. Luminescence will start and unlock.

EZ - IN: Unlock [[The Chariot ~REVIIVAL~]]
AT: Spoiler warning:

  • Unlock [[Distorted Fate]]
  • Get an S rank or higher on DESTRUCTION 3,2,1 [IN]

Distorted Fate.unlock:
EZ - IN: Spoiler warning:
  1. Play [[Luminescence]], full combo the section with the dimmed background, and reach (685k points for EZ, 679k for HD and 785k for IN) before the final drop. Fireworks should appear during the final drop if done correctly.
  2. [[Retribution]] will automatically start, with the addition of a health gauge that comes in at the first drop. Survive until the gauge freezes at the start of the second drop. After the end of the song, Distorted Fate will start and unlock.
AT: Get an S rank or higher on Distorted Fate [IN]

Random#R.title: Random <small>[R] - Alt Futur</small>
Random#R.unlock:
''Spoiler warning:''
  • Select Random in the song selection menu and hold down the Random button.
  • A [[Random#Takes|take]] will play at random, with the charter displayed as "Random()".
    • You may encounter a take you've already unlocked or the normal take with this method.
    • To tell which take you're playing, you can:
      • Get to the point where the takes differ.
      • Take note of how many points you're getting per note.
      • Look at the title of the song in the end screen, which will have a letter representing the take in grey color and square brackets.
  • After encountering a take, you can replay that take at any time by tapping its corresponding letter on the jacket.
